Random Pie Walker.

This recipe decides which way to go based on the mixing bowl.

Ingredients.
78 g north
83 g south
69 g east
87 g west
1 g counter

Method.
Take counter from refrigerator
Put north into the mixing bowl
Put south into the mixing bowl
Put east into the mixing bowl
Put west into the mixing bowl
Mix the mixing bowl well
Fold counter into the mixing bowl
Liquefy counter
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish
Refrigerate

Serves 1.
